# Shared JDBC drivers for the corporate MSR base image.
#
# This directory is empty in source control. CI populates it from the
# corporate artifact repository before invoking `docker build` so that
# the resulting wm-msr-base image contains the Oracle / Postgres /
# MSSQL drivers that downstream microservices share.
#
# Drivers placed here land at runtime under:
#   /opt/softwareag/IntegrationServer/instances/default/packages/
#     WmJDBCAdapter/code/jars
#
# Do not commit binary JARs to git -- they are licensed and version
# controlled in the artifact repository, not here.
